In Weekly Chart

Weekly 20 EMA crosses 60 EMA. Buy - check Resistance ,   
			-- If crossed down below 20 EMA Sell.
				-- Now, if then price crosses 20 EMA then buy (Provided 60 EMA is below 20 EMA)

